::K-9::

The transport ship Nova landed outfront the CF. The DNA scanner poped
up, and did its job. A form was found, and the scanner went down again.
The ships cockpit opens, and the new bot stept out. He didn't want to go
in, without permission. He opened another comm.
"Hello, I am outside the Ark. Would a high ranking officer come out?"
